14:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"KBYU kalkulyatori maqsadga qarab — vaznni saqlash, oriqlamoq yoki mushak massasini oshirish — kunlik kaloriya, oqsil, yog' va uglevodlar normasini hisoblaydi. JSST tavsiyalari bo'yicha BYU standart nisbati: 25-35% oqsillar, 20-35% yog'lar, 45-65% uglevodlar. An'anaviy yuqori uglevodli ratsion (guruch, non, xamir) bilan o'zbek aholisi uchun makronutrientlar balansi alohida ahamiyatga ega."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Qanday hisoblash kerak: avval kunlik kaloriya normasini aniqlang (Mifflin-San Jeor formulasi). Keyin makronutrientlar bo'yicha taqsimlang: 1 g oqsil = 4 kkal, 1 g yog' = 9 kkal, 1 g uglevod = 4 kkal. 80 kg erkak uchun misol, saqlash (2 400 kkal): oqsillar 30% = 720 kkal = 180 g; yog'lar 25% = 600 kkal = 67 g; uglevodlar 45% = 1 080 kkal = 270 g."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbek oshxonasi uchun KBYU moslashuvi: bir porsiya osh (400 g) ~40 g oqsil, 35 g yog', 90 g uglevod o'z ichiga oladi. Somsa — 15 g oqsil, 20 g yog', 30 g uglevod. Kabob (200 g) — 35 g oqsil, 15 g yog', 0 g uglevod. Lag'mon — 20 g oqsil, 15 g yog', 60 g uglevod. Taomlarning KBYUsini bilib, odatiy mahsulotlardan muvozanatli ratsion tuzish mumkin."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Oriqlamoq uchun tavsiya etiladi: oqsil ulushini 35-40% ga oshirish (kaloriya defitsitida mushaklar saqlanishiga yordam beradi), uglevodlarni 30-35% ga kamaytirish, yog'larni 25-30% da qoldirish. Mushak massasini oshirish uchun: oqsillar 30%, uglevodlar 50-55%, yog'lar 20%. Faol mashg'ulotlarda oqsilga ehtiyoj tana massasining 1 kg iga 1,8-2,2 g gacha ortadi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Saytimizda KBYU kalkulyatori shaxsiy normani avtomatik hisoblaydi: jins, yosh, bo'y, vazn, faollik darajasi va maqsadni kiriting. Kuniga aniq oqsillar, yog'lar va uglevodlar gramm miqdorini olasiz. Maksimal aniq natija uchun kaloriya kalkulyatori bilan birgalikda foydalaning."}]]}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Ko'p beriladigan savollar"}],["$","$L19",null,{"className":"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card px-4","children":[["$","$L1a","0",{"value":"faq-0","children":[["$","$L1b",null,{"className":"text-left text-foreground","children":"Qanday BYU nisbati optimal?"}],["$","$L1c",null,{"children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted-foreground","children":"Saqlash: oqsillar 30%, yog'lar 25%, uglevodlar 45%. Oriqlamoq: oqsillar 35-40%, uglevodlar 30-35%. Massa oshirish: uglevodlar 50-55%."}]}]]}],"$L1d","$L1e","$L1f","$L20"]}]]}],"$L21"]}]
